ADDRESSABLES SETUP GUIDE

1. Install Addressables Package
   - Window > Package Manager
   - Search "Addressables"
   - Install

2. Create Addressables Settings
   - Window > Asset Management > Addressables > Groups
   - Click "Create Addressables Settings"

3. Mark Level Scenes as Addressables
   - Select all level scenes in Assets/Scenes (Level 1 to Level 12)
   - Right-click > Mark as Addressable
   - In Addressables Groups window, move levels to a new group called "Levels"

4. Configure Remote Build Path
   - In Addressables Groups window, select "Levels" group
   - Inspector > Advanced > Build & Load Paths
   - Set Build Path: RemoteBuildPath
   - Set Load Path: your CDN URL (e.g., https://yourcdn.com/bundles)

5. Build Addressables Content
   - Addressables Groups window > Build > New Build > Default Build Script
   - Upload generated files from ServerData folder to your CDN

6. Setup Scene
   MenuScene:
   - Add AddressablesLevelLoader prefab (empty GameObject with script)
   - Add SplashScreen Canvas with:
     * Panel (background)
     * Slider (progress bar)
     * TextMeshProUGUI (percentage text)
   - Assign references in AddressablesLevelLoader

   Level Buttons:
   - Add MenuLevelButton script to each level button
   - Set levelIndex (1, 2, 3, etc.)

7. Menu Scene stays local, Level scenes load from CDN via Addressables
